snippet.textDisplay: Aditya and Achint I can’t thank you enough for this song. This song activated some dormant dna data in me which urges me to fare the sea everytime I listen to this track. The churn of emotions, depth of the lyrics and Aditya’s reverberating call for adventure wants me to get on my boat and conquer the seas just like my coast-dwelling ancestors! While the lyrics also have an alternate meaning of taking charge of your emotional turmoil and finding the pearl of courage deep within you! What a complete ballad! Anyone who’s reading this going through a tough time, you’ll make it! Onward and upward, excelsior!
